Reclusa::

She didn't like being called little one, but she smiled at him because
she did relish in his ideas. "Ah, very well then. Proceed."  She laid
down on the table.  "One last thing. Once I am in the other bot,
you'll need to place my form in the pod and put me out so they may
find me."  She smiled, then frowned. She didn't like having to do
this, but her revenge seemed to demand it. "Uh, just what will I look
like when I finally wake up and what form will I transform into? I
want to be a little familiar with what I'll be so I don't give myself
away from the start." The cold table gave it's last bit a reasurance
to her before she would start her next adventure.
